Purpose - To store collectiom of multiple values of same data type
Operation on 1D array

    1) declare & initialize the array
          int data[] = new int [5];
          int data[] = {34,23,53,632,123,1,4,67,2,5};
          
    2) how to print all the elements from array?
          first option ==>  Index based for loop
          
          for(int i=0; i<data.length(); i++){
            System.out.println(data[i]);
           }
           
          second option ==> for each loop
          
          for(int a: data){
            System.out.println(a);
          }
          
     3) default value of arrays
     
          int data[] = new int [5:
          
